toString

public java.lang.String toString()
Returns a string object representing this AttributeDataType's value.

If this object represents the Char attribute data type, a string equal to "Char" is returned.

If this object represents the Number attribute data type, a string equal to "Number" is returned.

If this object represents the Integer attribute data type, a string equal to "Integer" is returned.

If this object represents the Date attribute data type, a string equal to "Date" is returned.
